Source Package Installation 

To untar the file, type: 
	gtar xvzf Chess_V1.0_src.tar.gz 

Navigate to the chess directory, then to the src directory: 
	cd chess 
	cd src 

Install the program: 
	make chess 

To run the program, navigate first to the bin directory: 
	cd ../bin 
	./chess 

More detailed instructions on the installation/uninstallation of this program can be found in the software specification manual.
